The,MySqlJS,API,allows,developers,to,access,MySQL,from,their,JavaScript,clients,It,removes,the,need,for,custom,server,code,to,handle,data,transfer,between,the,client,and,the,MySQL,database,This,API,is,designed,for,use,in,closed,source,environments,rather,than,public,websites,It,is,free,for,use,in,both,commercial,and,non,commercial,projects,without,usage,restrictions